const LightTheme = {
    secondaryBackgroundColor: "#F6F9FC",
    mainTextColor: "#111439",
    hoverTextColor: "#11143988",
    quoteTextColor: "#11143966",
    dottedLineColor: "linear-gradient(#EBEBEB 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%)",
    scrollColor: "#0f0",
    scrollDim1: "#0f0",
    scrollDim2: "#0f0",
    scrollDim3: "#494B6499",
  
    primaryBackgroundColor: "#FFFFFF",
    aboutIdColor: "#CDCDE3",
    pTextColor: "#494B64",
  
    viewMoreBtnColor: "#CDCDE3",
    viewMoreBtnHoverColor: "#A5ACD9",
    projectIconColor: "#DADDED",
    projectIconHoverColor: "#A5ACD9",
    constructionTextColor: "#494B6433",
  
    copyrightTextColor: "#494B64688",
    madeWithTextColor: "#757796ee",

    transition: " 0.0s ease-in-out",
  };
  
  const DarkTheme = {
    secondaryBackgroundColor: "#15161A",
    mainTextColor: "#F6F9FC",
    hoverTextColor: "#F6F9FC88",
    quoteTextColor: "#9699AF99",
    dottedLineColor: "linear-gradient(#1B1C22 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%)",
    scrollColor: "#f00",
    scrollDim1: "#2E303D44",
    scrollDim2: "#2E303D77",
    scrollDim3: "#2E303D99",
  
    primaryBackgroundColor: "#121212",
    aboutIdColor: "#2E2F3F",
    pTextColor: "#9699AFdd",
  
    viewMoreBtnColor: "#373743",
    viewMoreBtnHoverColor: "#6E6F7C",
    projectIconColor: "#2E2F3F",
    projectIconHoverColor: "#51525F",
    constructionTextColor: "#494B6477",
  
    copyrightTextColor: "#65687A",
    madeWithTextColor: "#494B6477",

    transition: " 0.2s ease",
  };

  const themes = {
      light: LightTheme,
      dark: DarkTheme,
  }

  export default themes;

  //#535566 old made with dark
